e with God I am his when ever he wants as for the Devil he said that i am not welcome down below.", "author": "STIDGIT64", "created": 1782975250557, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "thegoldencalf", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "SO WHAT IS THE BIG DEAL", "last_comment_created": 1782988507066, "content": "<p>So Bitch McConnell had a heart attack supposedly well hell i had 2 back in 2001 and in fact i actually got to watch the machine flat line on my second one and was told if i had not been in the emergency i would have died as there was no way any emergency  service could have gotten to me in time if i had been any where else.\nSo as my insurance plans say let his ass die there is no need to waste money on him at 84 years of age. The insurance i pay for will not cover a sleep study for me even though i stop breathing when i sleep.\nOh and people do not worry i have made peace with God I am his when ever he wants as for the Devil he said that i am not welcome down below.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 24, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBhMRPQQ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 14, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8709622, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1782987163810, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment